### ERROR TIPS

- **Inventory full when harvesting:** The agent attempted to harvest when its inventory was full. Ensure the inventory has sufficient space before attempting to harvest.
- **Could not extract iron-plate at (0.0, 0.0):** The agent attempted to extract iron-plate from a location where no entity containing iron-plate exists. Verify the presence of the desired resource at the target location before attempting to extract it.
